   SONY-EARNINGS (Tokyo) _ The Sony Corp. says second-quarter
profit fell 12 percent hurt by the strong yen and by slowing sales
of its PlayStation videogame machines. Still, the results were
better than expected. By Stephanie Strom.
</P>
