<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-27 16:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0205 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l BC-WEEKEND-RETREAT-ART-N     10-27 1022
