supply and demand, the Coca-Cola Co. has quietly begun testing a
vending machine that can automatically raise prices for its soft
drinks in hot weather. By Constance L. Hays.
</P>
<P>
   ARMENIA-ATTACK (Moscow) _ Gunmen proclaiming a coup d'etat
stormed the parliament in Armenia's capital city of Yerevan on
Wednesday, killing the nation's prime minister, parliament speaker
and a number of senior legislators before seizing an unknown number
of hostages. Developing. By Michael Wines.
</P>
<P>
   IMMIG-LABOR-RIGHTS (Undated) _ The Equal Employment Opportunity
Commission announced this week that it would for the first time
extend broad anti-discrimination rights to illegal immigrants to
protect them if employers fire them or otherwise discriminate
against them because of their race, sex, age or religion. By Steven
Greenhouse.
</P>
