   NOTE: Drawing captioned ``SEALING ATTIC DOOR WITH INSULATED
WOODEN BOX'' goes with this column.
</P>
<P>
   CAPTION: Insulated box that fits over fold-down attic stairway
will served to conserve heat and seal out cold drafts.
</P>
