<DOCNO> NYT19991027.0314 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-27 19:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0407 &Cx1f; tib-z
