<HEADLINE>
LOS ANGELES DAILY NEWS SPORTS BUDGET
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
 
 
Stories for AMs and PMs of Oct. 28. Any questions or rerun
requests, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
FBC-UCLA (Los Angeles) _ Analysis of UCLA's disappointing season. 
By Jon Wilner. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-USC (Los Angeles) _ Analysis of USC's disappointing season. 
By Scott Wolf. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column on USC quarterback Mike
Van Raaphorst. 
