<HEADLINE>
SUPREME COURT TO REVIEW USE OF ELECTRIC CHAIR 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Attn: Fla., Ala., Ga., Neb., Ohio, S.C., Va., N.Y.)   (af)  
 By BILL DEDMAN   
